SIIS Strategy/Scalper Indicator Information System 2.0
======================================================

Installation
------------

1) Create a C++ virtual env :

Follow the instructions contained in file cmake/README.
And then activate it before building.

Then build and install TA-Lib :

$ cd third/ta-lib
$ ./configure
$ make
$ make install

$ deactivate  # or open another terminal (deactivate is not implemanted)

2) Create a PIP virtual env :
$ python -m venv siis.venv

Install the python dependencies :

$ source siis.venv/bin/activate
$ pip install -r requirements.txt
$ deactivate  # or keep it to start a connector


Configuration
-------------

First running will create a .siis folder on Linux based systems, and into User/APPDATA/siis on Windows.

strategy.json
#############

Follow the instructions from the file strategies/README.


connectors/
###########

Follow the instructions from the file connectors/README.


Running connectors
------------------

Follow the instructions from the file connectors/README.


Running strategies
------------------

Follow the instructions from the file strategies/README.

